<paragraph blockId="118.[313,1268,1377,1465]" box="[313,433,1377,1401]" pageId="118" pageNumber="622">
<emphasis box="[313,433,1377,1401]" italics="true" pageId="118" pageNumber="622">Etymology</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="118.[313,1268,1377,1465]" pageId="118" pageNumber="622">
The species is named after my granddaughter Samantha Climie, who lives at the 
<typeStatus box="[313,361,1441,1465]" pageId="118" pageNumber="622">type</typeStatus>
locality.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="118.[313,912,1508,1563]" box="[313,912,1508,1563]" pageId="118" pageNumber="622">
<emphasis box="[313,421,1508,1531]" italics="true" pageId="118" pageNumber="622">Diagnosis</emphasis>
